                    <i></i>
                    <p>Payment "On Account" is available to credit-approved Retailer Partners and may be subject to minimum order quantities and amounts. <b>On Account orders are not eligible for Free Shipping or earning of Smarter Reward Points. (Previously earned Smarter Rewards may be redeemed.)</p>
